  <summary date="2021-08-21T01:44:17Z" status="Introduced in House">Promoting Access to Diabetic Shoes Act

This bill allows a nurse practitioner or physician assistant to fulfill documentation requirements for coverage, under Medicare,&#160;of special shoes for diabetic individuals. Under current law, such requirements may be satisfied only by a physician.</summary>
